translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今のはお前を試しただけだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What just happened was only a test for you."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……昔から母殿に言われてることがあってな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...There is something my mother has told me since long ago.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 目の前で折るような奴！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Someone who would break it right in front of me!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そんな馬鹿がオレの味方になる奴だ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That kind of fool is someone who will be my ally!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そいつの言うことだけは聞いておけ！　とな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You should only listen to what they say! That's what I was told."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ごめん、意味分かんない……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sorry, I don't understand what it means..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 毛利家ってのは一族揃って馬鹿だから……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Mouri family, as a whole clan, are fools..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 馬鹿でなくば毛利の男とは言えん！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you're not a fool, you can't be called a Mouri man!"
And you are also a fool!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「オレはお前が気に入ったぞ……」

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "If by chance you show a pitiful attitude,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 恥ずかしい姿をオレに晒してみろ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: a shameful sight, sparing your life before me!
At that time, I will kill you!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それでも良ければ、オレを連れてけ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If that's alright with you, take me with you!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うっはははははははははははは！」
馬鹿というか破天荒というか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Are not so much fools as wild and unconventional...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そういう人間が好きだから……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's why I like those kinds of people...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「割と波長、合っちゃったのかも」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Maybe our wavelengths matched quite well.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あんまりランスに似てないと思ったけど、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I thought it didn't resemble Rance very much,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 案外ああいうとこは、近いのかも
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but surprisingly, in that way, they might be similar.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「魔王ってどんな人なんすか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "What kind of person is the Demon King...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「暴れるしか能のない男だが！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "He's a man who only knows how to rampage!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 暴れるだけなら天下無双！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When it comes to rampaging, he's unmatched across the land!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 毛利元就！　これより旅の共をする！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mouri Motonari! From now on, we will travel together!"

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The heir of the Mouri family, Mouri Motonari, has joined the party.
